CHANGELOG

v1.0.0 - SNIT
- Forked from PanIndustrial-Org/ICRC_fungible
- Implemented SNIT non-transferable engagement token
- Added Dave (partner app) registration and approval system
- Added principal linking (BagOfSnit) for multi-wallet support
- Added user level and XP system with mint multipliers
- Added affinity tracking for user-Dave relationships
- Added snit_mint and snit_purchase operations
- Enforced non-transferability via can_transfer hook
- Removed generic Token.mo, snstest.mo, and example files

v0.0.7 (upstream)
- update dependencies, compiler, dfx

v0.0.6 (upstream)
- implemented ICRC3 to include legacy get_transactions backfill
- added icrc-103 endpoint for retrieving allowances
- added icrc-106 endpoint for retrieving index canister
- added sns token to match interface and initialization as close to rust sns ledger as possible
